      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1284582737,
      "version": 729,
      "versionNonce": 1275059816,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1771025195493,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Notes:\n\n- Types that store data directly\n- Copied when passed to a function\n\n\nTypes:\n\n- int | int8 | int16 | int32 | int64\n- rune (Alias for int32)\n- uint | uint8 | uint16 | uint32 | uint64\n- byte (Alias for uint8)\n- uintptr (Alias for uint)\n- float32 | float64\n- complex64 | complex128\n- bool\n- Arrays\n- Structs and Interfaces",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Notes:\n\n- Types that store data directly\n- Copied when passed to a function\n\n\nTypes:\n\n- int | int8 | int16 | int32 | int64\n- rune (Alias for int32)\n- uint | uint8 | uint16 | uint32 | uint64\n- byte (Alias for uint8)\n- uintptr (Alias for uint)\n- float32 | float64\n- complex64 | complex128\n- bool\n- Arrays\n- Structs and Interfaces",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "TAoP0C7VHiXUKXcpmtmak",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 377.08453369140625,
      "y": -18.06170654296875,
      "width": 400.63946533203125,
      "height": 350,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "a7",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1300323121,
      "version": 878,
      "versionNonce": 1459484008,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1771025240117,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Notes:\n\n- Types that \"point\" to underlying data\n- Only the reference is copied when passed \nto a function. The underlying data is not.\n\nTypes:\n\n- string (immutable - behave like value type)\n- slice\n- map\n- func\n- chan\n- pointers",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Notes:\n\n- Types that \"point\" to underlying data\n- Only the reference is copied when passed \nto a function. The underlying data is not.\n\nTypes:\n\n- string (immutable - behave like value type)\n- slice\n- map\n- func\n- chan\n- pointers",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
